videos.headline: Newman sneaks in for Demon Deacons' first TD
videos.description: Jamie Newman runs the quarterback keeper and takes it in for a 5-yard Wake Forest touchdown to go up 7-0 over the Tar Heels.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Newman sneaks in for Demon Deacons' first TD) 2019/09/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Newman stretches out for 2nd rushing TD
videos.description: Jamie Newman keeps it and stretches out after he powers through the Tar Heels' defense to score his second rushing touchdown of the night.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Newman stretches out for 2nd rushing TD) 2019/09/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ref takes a tumble after being involved in tackle
videos.description: Umpire Danny Worrell is involved in a tackle and takes an athletic tumble in the aftermath.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ref takes a tumble after being involved in tackle) 2019/09/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: UNC scores late TD, gets 2-point conversion
videos.description: UNC's Sam Howell completes a pass to Dyami Brown for a touchdown, then Howell connects with Garrett Walston for the two-point conversion to cut the Wake Forest lead to 21-18.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (UNC scores late TD, gets 2-point conversion) 2019/09/13 ESHEET
